---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Anneliesa Liedle — romance-focused fiction writer based in Denver.">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-hero__grid">
        <div class="about-hero__image">
          <img src="/images/hero-banner.jpg" alt="Anneliesa Liedle" />
        </div>
        <div class="about-hero__content">
          <span class="about-hero__label">About the Author</span>
          <h1 class="animate-in animate-in--delay-1">Anneliesa Liedle</h1>
          <p class="about-hero__lead animate-in animate-in--delay-2">
            Romance-focused fiction writer based in Denver, Colorado.
            Currently querying a debut novel.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-body">
    <div class="container container--narrow">
      <div class="about-body__content">
        <p>
          I write character-driven stories where love isn't a destination — it's the
          thing that cracks people open and forces them to grow. My characters are
          messy, stubborn, and real. They don't fall into love so much as crash into it.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm drawn to stories that push back against harmful tropes — the ones that
          romanticize control, erase agency, or treat trauma as a personality trait.
          I believe romance can be intense, complicated, even dark, without being
          careless with the people in it.
        </p>
        <p>
          My work spans genres — from the gravel roads of international rally racing
          to dying generation ships to the Egyptian underworld — but the through-line
          is always the same: complicated people trying to be honest with each other,
          usually failing first, and earning something real by the end.
        </p>

        <h2>What I Write</h2>
        <ul class="about-list">
          <li><strong>Motorsport Romance</strong> — adrenaline, trust, and the intimacy of a two-person crew</li>
          <li><strong>Fantasy &amp; Sci-Fi Romance</strong> — world-building that serves the relationship, not the other way around</li>
          <li><strong>Dark Fantasy Romance</strong> — mythology reimagined, power dynamics examined, consent centered</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Beyond the Page</h2>
        <p>
          When I'm not writing, I'm probably watching rally highlights, researching
          obscure mythology, or convincing myself that the next chapter will be easier
          than the last one. I live in Denver with an ever-growing collection of
          half-finished notebooks and strong opinions about fictional people.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    padding-top: calc(80px + var(--space-2xl));
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-hero__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-hero__image img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .about-hero__label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--color-accent-text);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-hero__content h1 {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .about-hero__lead {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-body {
    padding: var(--space-xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .about-body__content p {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    max-width: none;
  }

  .about-body__content h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
  }

  .about-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .about-list li {
    padding: var(--space-md) 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-list li strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-hero__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .about-hero__image img {
      max-width: 300px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
